snippet.title: Akatori - Official Gameplay Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Akatori is an action platformer metroidvania developed by TeamNora Games. Players will embody Mako on an adventure to uncover the secrets of ancient gods, build friendships, and face powerful enemies by utilizing tight 2D controls across multiple realms. Akatori is coming soon to PC (Steam).

#Gaming #IGN #Games
